

‡¶è‡¶á ‡¶Ü‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶ï‡¶ø‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶ï‡¶ö‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ ‡¶´‡ßç‡¶≤‡ßã ‡¶∏‡¶¨ ‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡ßü ‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶•‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶≠‡ßá‡¶§‡¶∞‡ßá (Inward) ‡¶π‡ßü‡•§

üîÑ Registration Data Flow (Step-by-Step)

‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶õ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶≤‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∑‡ßç‡¶Ø ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶≤‡ßá ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶¨‡ßá‡¶® ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ ‡¶ï‡ßÄ‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá ‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶π‡¶ø‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞ (Web) ‡¶•‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶¶‡¶Æ ‡¶≠‡ßá‡¶§‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞ (Domain) ‡¶™‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶®‡ßç‡¶§ ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶π‡¶ø‡¶§ ‡¶π‡¶Ø‡¶º:

‡ßß. Web Layer (The Entry Point)
      User Action: ‡¶á‡¶â‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶â‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶Æ, ‡¶á‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶≤, ‡¶∂‡¶π‡¶∞ ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶∏‡¶ì‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶° ‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶ñ‡ßá 'Register' ‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶®‡•§
      ViewModel Mapping: ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶â‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶•‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶Ü‡¶∏‡¶æ ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ RegisterVm ‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶∏‡ßá ‡¶¨‡¶æ‡¶á‡¶®‡ßç‡¶° ‡¶π‡ßü ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç Data Annotations (‡¶Ø‡ßá‡¶Æ‡¶® [Required], [EmailAddress]) ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡ßü‡ßá ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶•‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶≠‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶°‡ßá‡¶∂‡¶® ‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶ï ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶æ ‡¶π‡ßü‡•§
      Controller Action: AccountController.cs ‡¶è‡¶∞ Register(vm) ‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶•‡¶°‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶ï‡¶≤ ‡¶π‡ßü‡•§ ‡¶è‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶á‡¶â‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ IP Address ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç User Agent ‡¶∏‡¶Ç‡¶ó‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶π ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§
      Service Call: ‡¶ï‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡ßã‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶æ ‡¶è‡¶á ‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶≠‡¶ø‡¶∏‡¶ü‡¶ø(IAuthService.RegisterAsync(...) ‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶•‡¶°‡¶ü‡¶ø) ‡¶ï‡ßÄ‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶ú ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá (Abstraction)‡•§ 
      Dependency Injection:  ‡¶∏‡ßá ‡¶∂‡ßÅ‡¶ß‡ßÅ IAuthService ‡¶á‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶´‡ßá‡¶∏‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶®‡ßá‡•§

‡ß®. Application Layer (The Orchestrator)
    ‡¶ï‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡ßã‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶§‡¶ñ‡¶® IAuthService ‡¶ï‡¶≤ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§ 
    ‡¶è‡¶á ‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶Æ‡ßÇ‡¶≤‡¶§ ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶ø "‡¶ï‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶ü" ‡¶¨‡¶æ ‡¶ö‡ßÅ‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶§‡¶ø‡¶∞ ‡¶Æ‡¶§‡ßã ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶ú ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§ 
    ‡¶è‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶¨‡¶≤‡ßá ‡¶¶‡ßá‡ßü "‡¶ï‡ßÄ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶π‡¶¨‡ßá", ‡¶ï‡¶ø‡¶®‡ßç‡¶§‡ßÅ "‡¶ï‡ßÄ‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶π‡¶¨‡ßá(Infrastructure Layer)" ‡¶§‡¶æ ‡¶è‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶æ‡•§
    Request Handling: ‡¶ï‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡ßã‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶ï‡¶≤‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶á‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶´‡ßá‡¶∏ ‡¶π‡ßü‡ßá Infrastructure ‡¶≤‡ßá‡ßü‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ AuthService ‡¶á‡¶Æ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶∂‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶™‡ßå‡¶Å‡¶õ‡¶æ‡ßü‡•§

‡ß©. Infrastructure Layer (The Doer)
‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá‡¶á ‡¶Ü‡¶∏‡¶≤ ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶ú ‡¶¨‡¶æ ‡¶≤‡¶ú‡¶ø‡¶ï‡¶ó‡ßÅ‡¶≤‡ßã ‡¶ò‡¶ü‡ßá:
    Duplicate Check: ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶•‡¶Æ‡ßá ‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶ï ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶è‡¶á ‡¶á‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶≤ ‡¶¶‡¶ø‡ßü‡ßá ‡¶Ö‡¶®‡ßç‡¶Ø ‡¶ï‡ßá‡¶â ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶ú‡¶ø‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶õ‡ßá ‡¶ï‡¶ø ‡¶®‡¶æ‡•§
    Account Number Generation: ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶á‡¶â‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡ß´-‡¶°‡¶ø‡¶ú‡¶ø‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Ö‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶â‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü ‡¶®‡¶Æ‡ßç‡¶¨‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡ßá‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶ü ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§
    Security: PasswordHasher ‡¶¨‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶¨‡¶π‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶á‡¶â‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶á‡¶® ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶∏‡¶ì‡ßü‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶°‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶è‡¶®‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶™‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶° (Hash) ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§    
    Domain Entity Creation: ‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶® ‡¶á‡¶®‡¶´‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶ö‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞ Domain Layer-‡¶è‡¶∞ Customer ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç Account ‡¶è‡¶®‡¶ü‡¶ø‡¶ü‡¶ø‡¶∞ ‡¶®‡¶§‡ßÅ‡¶® ‡¶Ö‡¶¨‡¶ú‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶ü ‡¶§‡ßà‡¶∞‡¶ø ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§

    Persistence: AppDbContext ‡¶è‡¶∞ ‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶ß‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶Æ‡ßá ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá‡¶∏‡ßá ‡¶∏‡ßá‡¶≠ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶∂ ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ì‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ ‡¶π‡¶Ø‡¶º‡•§

‡ß™. Domain Layer (The Core)
‡¶∏‡¶¨‡¶∂‡ßá‡¶∑‡ßá ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶ó‡ßÅ‡¶≤‡ßã Customer ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç Account ‡¶è‡¶®‡¶ü‡¶ø‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶π‡¶ø‡¶∏‡ßá‡¶¨‡ßá ‡¶§‡ßà‡¶∞‡¶ø ‡¶π‡¶Ø‡¶º‡•§ ‡¶è‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶∏‡¶ø‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶∏‡¶¨‡¶ö‡ßá‡¶Ø‡¶º‡ßá ‡¶∏‡ßÅ‡¶∞‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶∑‡¶ø‡¶§ ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶≠‡ßá‡¶§‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞‡•§
    ‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶ï‡ßã‡¶®‡ßã ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá‡¶∏ ‡¶¨‡¶æ ‡¶è‡¶á‡¶ö‡¶ü‡¶ø‡¶ü‡¶ø‡¶™‡¶ø (HTTP) ‡¶ú‡ßç‡¶û‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶æ‡•§
    ‡¶è‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶∂‡ßÅ‡¶ß‡ßÅ ‡¶á‡¶â‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶§‡¶•‡ßç‡¶Ø (Name, Email, Balance) ‡¶ß‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶£ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá‡•§



‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞ (Layer)  | ‡¶¶‡¶æ‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶ø‡¶§‡ßç‡¶¨ (Responsibility)
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Web (UI)	   | ‡¶á‡¶â‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶á‡¶®‡¶™‡ßÅ‡¶ü ‡¶®‡ßá‡¶ì‡ßü‡¶æ ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶ï‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡ßã‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶†‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßã‡•§
Application    | ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶ú‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶®‡¶ø‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶∂ ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ì‡ßü‡¶æ (Interfaces)‡•§
Infrastructure | ‡¶ï‡ßÄ‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶π‡¶¨‡ßá- ‡¶™‡¶æ‡¶∏‡¶ì‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶° ‡¶π‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶∂‡¶ø‡¶Ç, ‡¶Ö‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶â‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü ‡¶®‡¶Æ‡ßç‡¶¨‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡ßá‡¶®‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶ü ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç DB ‡¶∏‡ßá‡¶≠‡•§
Domain         | ‡¶Æ‡ßÇ‡¶≤ ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶Æ‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶Ö‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶â‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü ‡¶Ö‡¶¨‡¶ú‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶ü (Data Structure)‡•§
---------------------------------------------------------------------


========================================== CODES ==============================================================

Clean Architecture-‡¶è‡¶∞ ‡¶á‡¶®‡¶ì‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶° (Inward) ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ ‡¶´‡ßç‡¶≤‡ßã ‡¶Ö‡¶®‡ßÅ‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡ßü‡ßÄ ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶§‡¶ø‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶ï‡ßã‡¶°‡¶ó‡ßÅ‡¶≤‡ßã ‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶ú‡¶ø‡ßü‡ßá ‡¶¶‡ßá‡¶ì‡ßü‡¶æ ‡¶π‡¶≤‡ßã:

---

### ‡ßß. Web Layer (The Entry Point)

‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶á‡¶â‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶á‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶´‡ßá‡¶∏ ‡¶•‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßá ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ ‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶∏‡¶ø‡¶≠ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶æ ‡¶π‡ßü ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶•‡¶Æ‡¶ø‡¶ï ‡¶≠‡ßç‡¶Ø‡¶æ‡¶≤‡¶ø‡¶°‡ßá‡¶∂‡¶® ‡¶∂‡ßá‡¶∑‡ßá ‡¶∏‡¶æ‡¶∞‡ßç‡¶≠‡¶ø‡¶∏ ‡¶ï‡¶≤ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶æ ‡¶π‡ßü‡•§

ViewModel: `RegisterVm.cs`

public sealed class RegisterVm
{
    [Required, StringLength(100)]
    public string Name { get; set; } = "";

    [Required, EmailAddress]
    public string Email { get; set; } = "";

    [Required]
    public string Password { get; set; } = "";
    
    public string City { get; set; } = "";
}



Controller: `AccountController.cs`

public class AccountController : Controller
{
    private readonly IAuthService _auth; // Dependency Injection (Abstraction)

    public AccountController(IAuthService auth) => _auth = auth;

    [HttpPost]
    public async Task<IActionResult> Register(RegisterVm vm)
    {
        if (!ModelState.IsValid) return View(vm);

        var ip = HttpContext.Connection.RemoteIpAddress?.ToString() ?? "unknown";
        var ua = Request.Headers.UserAgent.ToString();

        // Service Call: ‡¶ï‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡ßã‡¶≤‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ú‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶®‡¶æ ‡¶è‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶ï‡ßÄ‡¶≠‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶ú ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá
        var res = await _auth.RegisterAsync(vm.Name, vm.Email, vm.Password, vm.City, ip, ua);

        if (!res.Success) return View(vm);
        return RedirectToAction("RegisterSuccess");
    }
}

```

---

### ‡ß®. Application Layer (The Orchestrator)

‡¶è‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶∂‡ßÅ‡¶ß‡ßÅ ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶ï‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶ü ‡¶¨‡¶æ ‡¶á‡¶®‡ßç‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶∞‡¶´‡ßá‡¶∏ ‡¶™‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶¶‡¶æ‡¶® ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡ßá, ‡¶Ø‡¶æ ‡¶¨‡¶≤‡ßá ‡¶¶‡ßá‡ßü "‡¶ï‡ßÄ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶§‡ßá ‡¶π‡¶¨‡ßá"‡•§

Interface: `IAuthService.cs`

```csharp
public interface IAuthService
{
    // ‡¶è‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶è‡¶ï‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶ö‡ßÅ‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶§‡¶ø (Contract)
    Task<Result<string>> RegisterAsync(string name, string email, string password, string city, string ip, string userAgent);
}


---

### ‡ß©. Infrastructure Layer (The Doer)

‡¶è‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá‡¶á ‡¶Ü‡¶∏‡¶≤ ‡¶≤‡¶ú‡¶ø‡¶ï, ‡¶∏‡¶ø‡¶ï‡¶ø‡¶â‡¶∞‡¶ø‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá‡¶∏ ‡¶∏‡ßá‡¶≠ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ï‡¶æ‡¶ú‡¶ó‡ßÅ‡¶≤‡ßã ‡¶∏‡¶Æ‡ßç‡¶™‡¶®‡ßç‡¶® ‡¶π‡ßü‡•§

Service Implementation: `AuthService.cs`

```csharp
public class AuthService : IAuthService
{
    private readonly AppDbContext _db;

    public async Task<Result<string>> RegisterAsync(...)
    {
        // 1. Duplicate Check
        if (await _db.Customers.AnyAsync(x => x.Email == email)) 
            return Result<string>.Fail("Email already exists.");

        // 2. Account Number Generation
        string acc = Random.Shared.Next(10000, 100000).ToString();

        // 3. Security (Password Hashing)
        var hash = PasswordHasher.Hash(password);

        // 4. Domain Entity Creation: ‡¶á‡¶®‡¶´‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßç‡¶∞‡¶æ‡¶ï‡¶ö‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶≤‡ßá‡¶Ø‡¶º‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶°‡ßã‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶á‡¶® ‡¶Ö‡¶¨‡¶ú‡ßá‡¶ï‡ßç‡¶ü ‡¶§‡ßà‡¶∞‡¶ø ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶õ‡ßá
        var customer = new Customer 
        { 
            Name = name, 
            Email = email, 
            AccountNumber = acc, 
            PasswordHash = hash,
            Account = new Account { Balance = 0m } 
        };

        // 5. Persistence: ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶¨‡ßá‡¶∏‡ßá ‡¶∏‡ßá‡¶≠ ‡¶ï‡¶∞‡¶æ
        _db.Customers.Add(customer);
        await _db.SaveChangesAsync();

        return Result<string>.Ok(acc);
    }
}


---

### ‡ß™. Domain Layer (The Core)

‡¶è‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶∏‡¶ø‡¶∏‡ßç‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶Æ‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶∏‡¶¨‡¶ö‡ßá‡ßü‡ßá ‡¶≠‡ßá‡¶§‡¶∞‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶Ö‡¶Ç‡¶∂, ‡¶Ø‡ßá‡¶ñ‡¶æ‡¶®‡ßá ‡¶∂‡ßÅ‡¶ß‡ßÅ ‡¶°‡¶æ‡¶ü‡¶æ‡¶∞ ‡¶ó‡¶†‡¶® ‡¶è‡¶¨‡¶Ç ‡¶Æ‡ßÇ‡¶≤ ‡¶¨‡¶ø‡¶ú‡¶®‡ßá‡¶∏ ‡¶è‡¶®‡¶ü‡¶ø‡¶ü‡¶ø ‡¶•‡¶æ‡¶ï‡ßá‡•§

Entity: `Customer.cs`

```csharp
namespace OnlineBanking.Domain.Entities;

public sealed class Customer
{
    public Guid Id { get; set; } = Guid.NewGuid();
    public string Name { get; set; } = "";
    public string Email { get; set; } = "";
    public string AccountNumber { get; set; } = ""; // ‡ß´-‡¶°‡¶ø‡¶ú‡¶ø‡¶ü‡ßá‡¶∞ ‡¶®‡¶Æ‡ßç‡¶¨‡¶∞
    public string PasswordHash { get; set; } = "";
    
    // Domain knows nothing about DB or HTTP
    public Account Account { get; set; } = new(); 
}

```

